FBIS4-28830 "dreas114_b_94002" FBIS-EAS-94-114 Daily Report 7 Jun 1994 Mongolia MONTSAME Carries Press Reviews MONTSAME Carries Press Reviews For 7 Jun BK0806023294 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1318 GMT 7 Jun 94 BK0806023294 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME English BFN [Text] Ulaanbaatar, June 7 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- The official newspaper "ARDIYN ERH" informs that at the spring session of the Great State Hural being on here there has been discussed the draft law on pensions and allowances. [sentence as received] The newspaper provides a telegram sent by J. Moravcik in reply to the Prime Minister of Mongolia P. Jasray with his gratitude for the congratulations in connection with his being appointed to the post of chairman of the Government of Slovakia It is reported that the Minister of External Relations of Mongolia T. Gombosuren participating in the 11th conference of foreign ministers of non-aligned countries has met in Cairo with the ministers on foreign affairs of Egypt, Philippines, Vietnam, Cambodia and Singapore and exchanged with them opinions on the issues of bilateral relations and international affairs. In its permanent heading -- "From Dawn to Dusk" the newspaper publishes some information concerning the events within the country. It is informed that the spring sowing campaign is completing in the Selenge Aimag being the main granary of the country, the ceremony of laying down the foundations of the monument to the legend. [sentence as received]
